Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.85,0:00:23.34,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}奴婢拜见将军
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.28,0:00:25.94,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}多谢将军挂怀
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.65,0:00:28.68,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}奴婢为将军献舞一段
Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.86,0:00:30.91,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}已谢将军厚意
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.09,0:00:32.82,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}小姐 请
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.36,0:01:40.22,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}貂蝉啊貂蝉
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.23,0:01:44.79,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}大汉之兴亡 老父之生死
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.56,0:01:47.83,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}全搁在你身上了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.07,0:01:50.80,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}你如是不能成功
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.10,0:01:53.33,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}必引来灭族之祸
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.51,0:01:56.20,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}老夫也将化做一碗血酒
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.61,0:02:00.57,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}被禽兽们开怀痛饮啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.32,0:02:44.38,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}请将军庄重
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.99,0:02:46.15,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}不要玷污了自己
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.00,0:02:52.90,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}在下失态了 请小姐恕罪
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.10,0:02:58.06,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}不不不 是奴婢怕玷污了将军
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.24,0:03:04.11,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}小姐是司徒大人的义女
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.54,0:03:06.07,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}怎么会玷污在下呢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.46,0:03:19.58,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}启禀将军 奴婢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.93,0:03:28.66,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}奴婢本是忠臣之后 皇亲后裔
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.60,0:03:37.30,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}因全家遭奸臣所害 满门抄斩
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.54,0:03:42.61,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}只有奴婢侥幸逃脱流落荒野
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.12,0:03:46.48,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}那一年的春天
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.59,0:03:50.05,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}司徒大人进山祭祖
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.59,0:03:55.19,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}焚香的时候山风吹起
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.60,0:04:00.22,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}一抹香灰落在了一个孤女身上
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.47,0:04:02.80,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}那就是奴婢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.87,0:04:09.67,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}司徒大人听了奴婢的身世
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.34,0:04:11.37,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}万分悲痛
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.31,0:04:17.08,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}并将奴婢带回府中收为义女
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.28,0:04:18.81,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}取名貂蝉
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.59,0:04:28.56,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}奴婢的身世无人知晓
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.06,0:04:34.09,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}将军对奴婢有救命之恩
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.47,0:04:39.06,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}奴婢不敢欺瞒将军
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.84,0:04:43.90,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}万想不到小姐如此尊贵
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.01,0:04:48.41,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}吕布匹夫竟然玷污了小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.12,0:04:49.81,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}死罪
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.28,0:04:52.38,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}不不不 将军言重了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.72,0:04:53.41,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}只是怕
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.82,0:04:56.22,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}董相国知道了奴婢的身世后
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.32,0:04:59.35,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}必将奴婢碎尸万段连累了将军
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.86,0:05:05.99,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}放心 有我吕布在就有小姐在
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.60,0:05:12.54,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}请小姐恕罪
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.67,0:05:14.00,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}自从与小姐相见以后
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.01,0:05:18.64,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}我无时无刻不在惦记小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.85,0:05:22.75,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}就连梦里都是小姐的身影
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.09,0:05:32.25,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}此生如不能长伴于小姐左右
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.99,0:05:34.93,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}生不如死
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.07,0:05:43.90,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}如能与小姐相伴终生
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.67,0:05:46.33,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}哪怕是片刻
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.04,0:05:49.34,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}虽死无憾
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.22,0:06:06.49,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}小姐 吕布离不开你
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.46,0:06:11.79,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}吕布要与小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.50,0:06:17.96,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}生死相依 白头到老
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.97,0:06:20.73,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}将军
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.67,0:06:24.58,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}请将军快快请起 万万使不得
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.38,0:06:28.68,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}小姐不答应我就不起来
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.49,0:06:38.95,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}将军还是起来吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.10,0:06:47.09,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}小姐是答应了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.31,0:07:01.27,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}将军对小女子有救命之恩
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.18,0:07:04.58,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}小女子无以回报
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.12,0:07:08.78,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}只要将军
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.66,0:07:12.62,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}只要将军不嫌弃奴婢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.46,0:07:20.66,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}不过 此事要向义父禀报
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.03,0:07:22.47,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}对
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.74,0:07:24.73,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}对对对
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.30,0:07:27.47,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}我这就向司徒大人提亲去
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.25,0:07:35.61,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}吕布拜见义父大人
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.15,0:07:39.88,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}将军你 你 你这是怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.59,0:07:43.52,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}将军 你的义父是董相国
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.82,0:07:46.35,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}老夫岂敢僭越呀
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.53,0:07:47.82,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}拜董相国为义父
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.93,0:07:50.99,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}不过是求个晋身之道罢了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.57,0:07:54.76,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}拜你为义父
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.63,0:07:57.97,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}才是至真至切之情
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.14,0:08:01.94,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}那你为何拜我为义父呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.41,0:08:03.81,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}请义父恩准
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.81,0:08:07.80,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}把貂蝉嫁给我为妻
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.35,0:08:14.32,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}貂蝉 貂蝉
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.52,0:08:17.22,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}你在哪儿呢 给我滚进来
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.46,0:08:21.22,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}小女拜见义父
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.36,0:08:22.62,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}你这个死丫头
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.10,0:08:25.43,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}全不知礼法
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.90,0:08:28.92,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}也不想一想你是什么人哪
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.34,0:08:31.03,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}区区一个小女子
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.50,0:08:34.44,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}你怎么能够配得上吕将军呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.58,0:08:43.14,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}一定是你勾引将军坏我家风
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.45,0:08:44.35,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}义父
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.39,0:08:52.29,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}吕将军 小女貂蝉配不上你啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.76,0:08:53.82,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}司徒大人
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.43,0:08:58.73,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}你是说我吕布配不上貂蝉吗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.63,0:09:01.90,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}将军为何如此说话
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.30,0:09:03.43,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}我已经知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.00,0:09:06.73,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}貂蝉原本是忠良之后
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.94,0:09:08.93,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}金枝玉叶
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.41,0:09:10.67,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}而我吕布在你眼里
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.41,0:09:14.00,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}不过是一个鲁莽匹夫
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.85,0:09:21.22,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}在你眼里我吕布配不上貂蝉
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.39,0:09:22.68,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}不不不不 绝不
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.02,0:09:28.48,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}老夫素来认为将军是勇冠天下
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.63,0:09:29.99,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}忠义双全
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.50,0:09:35.33,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}既然如此 请把貂蝉许配给我
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.17,0:09:42.87,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}老夫膝下无子
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.28,0:09:46.44,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}只有这么一个义女
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.98,0:09:51.68,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}我待她可比亲闺女还要亲哪
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.32,0:09:55.15,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}如果把貂蝉许配我为妻
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.36,0:09:57.98,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}我自然事大人如父
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.46,0:10:04.19,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}此生此世愿与貂蝉白头到老
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.40,0:10:06.49,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}与义父荣辱与共
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.43,0:10:10.87,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}将军所说当真
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.57,0:10:15.10,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}吕布向皇天后土立誓
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.34,0:10:18.04,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}此生此世愿与貂蝉白头到老
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.34,0:10:19.81,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}与义父荣辱与共
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.21,0:10:21.41,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}有违此誓
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.51,0:10:25.92,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}天诛地灭 万载不复
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.69,0:10:29.35,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}请义父准许我们成婚吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.69,0:10:31.85,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}义父
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.23,0:10:38.22,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}好吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.00,0:10:48.70,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}那老夫就把貂蝉托付给将军了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.91,0:10:57.91,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}谢义父
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.20,0:11:17.23,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}将军 二更天了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.14,0:11:21.80,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}将军你该回府了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.91,0:11:24.74,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}我舍不下小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.63,0:11:41.53,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}有了这根银簪
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.49,0:11:46.86,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}就像是将军陪在我的身边
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.40,0:11:49.37,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}吕布枉活了半世
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.47,0:11:53.44,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}现在才算尝到了活着的滋味
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.08,0:12:01.41,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}我恨不能
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.58,0:12:06.55,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}永远都沉醉在小姐的芬芳中
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.19,0:12:12.95,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}将军虽然与小女已经定情
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.49,0:12:16.55,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}今晚也不便留宿
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.00,0:12:17.98,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}老夫觉得
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.60,0:12:21.59,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}你们还是该通过正常的婚嫁
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.03,0:12:25.00,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}结为百年之好为佳
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.20,0:12:28.76,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}这样也配得上将军的英名啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.74,0:12:30.67,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}义父说的是
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.38,0:12:34.81,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}那么七天之后
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.15,0:12:37.41,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}我便遣人送来礼金与婚书
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.55,0:12:39.31,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}与小姐正式定亲
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.85,0:12:44.99,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}然后择吉日行婚礼迎娶小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.99,0:12:45.02,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}然后择吉日行婚礼迎娶小姐 好恭喜将军
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.02,0:12:47.15,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}好 恭喜将军
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.19,0:12:51.09,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}老夫能有将军为婿
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.80,0:12:54.27,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}我这终生有靠啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.10,0:12:57.16,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}不过这事
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.34,0:13:01.24,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}暂时还是不要让相国知道
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.41,0:13:02.67,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}为何
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.44,0:13:06.28,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}相国是将军的义父
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.71,0:13:10.44,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}万一相国不允许这门亲事
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.52,0:13:12.28,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}不就麻烦了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.99,0:13:18.05,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}我想不如等木已成舟之后
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.36,0:13:20.42,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}再禀报相国
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.99,0:13:25.09,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}当然 如何定夺听将军的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.13,0:13:26.83,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}请将军斟酌
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.10,0:13:31.09,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}义父说得是 那就这么办吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.24,0:13:32.17,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}好
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.51,0:13:34.44,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}请
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.26,0:14:00.36,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}小女拜见义父
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.30,0:14:07.57,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}老夫替天下苍生请命
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.14,0:14:13.48,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}求女儿救救大汉吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.28,0:14:15.47,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}义父快快请起
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.21,0:14:17.65,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}你已经跟我说过了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.08,0:14:19.48,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}我也答应了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.75,0:14:20.91,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}你不是已经把女儿
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.09,0:14:23.32,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}许配给吕将军了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.92,0:14:29.59,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}那只是老夫的一道计谋
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.73,0:14:30.85,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}计谋
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.63,0:14:34.10,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}是啊 计谋
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.00,0:14:37.56,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}而且只是计谋的一半
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.67,0:14:42.70,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}此计若要成功必须是连环计
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.48,0:14:48.74,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}义父你还是快快请起吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.88,0:14:51.47,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}你这样和我说话
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.05,0:14:54.18,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}我害怕
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.02,0:15:01.32,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}不 老父这道连环计龌龊不堪哪
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.26,0:15:04.69,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}老父无颜起身
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.86,0:15:08.42,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}只能跪着跟女儿说了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.44,0:15:12.06,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}义父请讲
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.04,0:15:20.54,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}天下大乱 祸首董卓
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.98,0:15:22.74,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}若要除掉董卓
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.15,0:15:26.64,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}必须靠吕布相助啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.95,0:15:30.41,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}但那董卓待吕布甚厚
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.59,0:15:32.52,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}若要二人反目
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.49,0:15:37.83,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}那只有靠 靠女儿你了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.47,0:15:44.87,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}我
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.01,0:15:49.00,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}我能做什么
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.18,0:15:56.08,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}我要把你献给董卓
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.45,0:16:02.39,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}女儿 女儿
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.52,0:16:05.55,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}女儿天生丽质 美若天仙
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.72,0:16:07.21,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}见者无不心动
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.33,0:16:10.76,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}更何况那好色之徒董卓
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.63,0:16:13.93,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}董卓一旦喜欢上你
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.77,0:16:17.96,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}那吕布必然悲愤万分
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.54,0:16:21.37,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}他本是个率真的男儿
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.54,0:16:23.03,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}爱恨鲜明
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.21,0:16:26.18,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}任谁夺了他心爱之人
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.34,0:16:29.04,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}必和他结下生死大恨
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.15,0:16:33.48,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}甚至会伺机刺杀董卓
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.59,0:16:40.62,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}如此 天下可定 大汉得救了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.69,0:16:43.72,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}义父
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.33,0:16:51.13,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}义父要把我献给那个禽兽
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.37,0:16:58.61,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}若除禽兽必先献身于禽兽啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.92,0:17:10.41,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}义父此举与禽兽何异
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.82,0:17:15.62,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}是啊 是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.43,0:17:20.99,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}老夫此计龌龊不堪
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.40,0:17:22.76,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}这事
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.07,0:17:28.80,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}我更知道女儿有多么地受折磨
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.21,0:17:36.51,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}但是灭贼兴汉非此不可啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.25,0:17:39.62,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}女儿啊 我求你了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.75,0:17:44.15,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}求你为大汉献身哪
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.55,0:18:14.18,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}女儿 女儿 女儿啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.06,0:18:24.46,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}苍天哪 先帝啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.52,0:18:51.96,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.29,0:18:56.32,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}主公还是水米不进
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.50,0:19:00.99,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}今天已经是第五天了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.50,0:19:06.10,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}在下求小姐劝劝主公吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.20,0:19:39.19,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}自从与小姐相见以后
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.77,0:19:43.76,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}我无时无刻不在惦念着小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.41,0:19:50.68,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}就连 就连梦里都是小姐的身影
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.79,0:20:01.95,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}此生若不能常伴于小姐左右
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.80,0:20:05.52,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}生不如死
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.30,0:20:08.09,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.87,0:20:13.27,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}主公水米未进已经是第七天了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.01,0:20:15.44,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}奴才觉得
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.34,0:20:19.54,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}主公怕是熬不过今晚了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.23,0:20:45.36,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}义父 吃饭吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.84,0:20:55.01,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}女儿 你答应老父了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.29,0:21:08.42,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}议政毕 退朝
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.67,0:21:19.54,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}恭送相国
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.95,0:21:34.58,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}老臣给相国请安
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.82,0:21:39.15,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}王允 难得你给咱家请安哪
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.72,0:21:40.75,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}难得难得
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.73,0:21:43.28,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}你有何事啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.87,0:21:48.36,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}都退了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.87,0:21:50.99,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}遵命
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.84,0:21:58.14,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}王允哪 说吧
Dialogue: 0,0:22:00.08,0:22:04.14,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}臣寒舍有几株百年梅花
Dialogue: 0,0:22:04.35,0:22:06.15,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}近日正在盛开
Dialogue: 0,0:22:06.38,0:22:09.95,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}老臣想请相国大人
Dialogue: 0,0:22:10.22,0:22:15.56,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}于明日光临寒舍 饮酒赏梅
Dialogue: 0,0:22:16.06,0:22:17.19,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}什么
Dialogue: 0,0:22:18.56,0:22:20.93,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}你要请咱家喝酒
Dialogue: 0,0:22:21.73,0:22:22.72,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}正是
Dialogue: 0,0:22:23.50,0:22:27.94,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}相国为国操劳臣等无不敬佩
Dialogue: 0,0:22:28.71,0:22:30.83,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}老臣想借此表达
Dialogue: 0,0:22:30.98,0:22:34.43,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}对相国的感激之心
Dialogue: 0,0:22:36.11,0:22:38.81,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}好好好 不瞒你说
Dialogue: 0,0:22:39.15,0:22:41.45,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}咱家是总想着
Dialogue: 0,0:22:41.79,0:22:43.88,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}多和你们这些公卿大臣们
Dialogue: 0,0:22:44.09,0:22:45.56,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}交往交往
Dialogue: 0,0:22:45.72,0:22:48.75,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}可你呢 就是不请咱家喝酒
Dialogue: 0,0:22:49.56,0:22:51.19,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}咱家还以为你啊
Dialogue: 0,0:22:51.30,0:22:53.76,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}看不上咱家呢
Dialogue: 0,0:22:53.90,0:22:55.42,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}臣岂敢
Dialogue: 0,0:22:55.77,0:22:59.46,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}老臣是怕相国不肯赏光啊
Dialogue: 0,0:22:59.67,0:23:01.16,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}哪里 哪里啊
Dialogue: 0,0:23:01.27,0:23:03.24,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}这个光咱家是赏定了
Dialogue: 0,0:23:03.34,0:23:07.33,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}不 这个梅花咱家是赏定了
Dialogue: 0,0:23:08.28,0:23:10.25,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}你说是什么时候
Dialogue: 0,0:23:10.78,0:23:12.68,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}明日正午
Dialogue: 0,0:23:12.98,0:23:14.45,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}干嘛明日正午啊
Dialogue: 0,0:23:14.92,0:23:16.91,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}今天不行吗
Dialogue: 0,0:23:17.09,0:23:19.35,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}就今天嘛 你这样
Dialogue: 0,0:23:20.83,0:23:23.09,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}回去把酒赶快准备好
Dialogue: 0,0:23:23.56,0:23:26.03,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}咱家即刻就到
Dialogue: 0,0:23:27.33,0:23:31.46,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}感激相国 老臣遵命
Dialogue: 0,0:23:31.67,0:23:33.10,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}请请请
Dialogue: 0,0:23:59.43,0:24:02.52,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}老臣恭迎相国
Dialogue: 0,0:24:09.41,0:24:13.90,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}王允啊 这就是你府上
Dialogue: 0,0:24:13.98,0:24:15.21,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}是
Dialogue: 0,0:24:15.48,0:24:21.89,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}太简陋了 太简陋了
Dialogue: 0,0:24:22.92,0:24:24.98,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}住这么简陋的房子
Dialogue: 0,0:24:25.09,0:24:26.06,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}怎么能配得上你
Dialogue: 0,0:24:26.19,0:24:27.99,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}司徒大人的尊贵啊
Dialogue: 0,0:24:28.46,0:24:29.89,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}哪里 哪里
Dialogue: 0,0:24:29.96,0:24:31.05,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}等着
Dialogue: 0,0:24:31.26,0:24:34.70,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}将来咱家要赏你一座大宅子
Dialogue: 0,0:24:34.93,0:24:36.92,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}老臣不敢 不敢
Dialogue: 0,0:24:39.50,0:24:42.94,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}奴婢拜见相国
Dialogue: 0,0:24:49.08,0:24:50.95,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}这 这是
Dialogue: 0,0:24:54.55,0:24:57.08,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}这这这 这是
Dialogue: 0,0:24:57.29,0:24:59.52,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}这是小女貂蝉
Dialogue: 0,0:25:07.90,0:25:09.33,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}王允哪 王允哪
Dialogue: 0,0:25:09.50,0:25:12.37,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}你是金屋藏娇啊
Dialogue: 0,0:25:12.57,0:25:15.60,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}你看你看 就是这洛阳长安两都
Dialogue: 0,0:25:15.81,0:25:18.71,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}都找不出这么一个仙人来啊
Dialogue: 0,0:25:19.98,0:25:22.14,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}好 好
Dialogue: 0,0:25:24.28,0:25:26.22,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}好 好好好
Dialogue: 0,0:25:26.35,0:25:30.52,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}貂蝉 还不快去搀扶相国入内
Dialogue: 0,0:25:34.06,0:25:35.82,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}好好 好
Dialogue: 0,0:25:37.30,0:25:39.20,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}相国请
Dialogue: 0,0:25:41.80,0:25:43.49,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}不不不 不
Dialogue: 0,0:25:43.97,0:25:46.73,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}还是让咱家来搀扶你吧
Dialogue: 0,0:25:46.94,0:25:51.00,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}来来来 咱家来搀扶小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:25:58.22,0:25:59.77,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}请
Dialogue: 0,0:27:11.62,0:27:14.46,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}相国 请饮
Dialogue: 0,0:27:34.61,0:27:35.77,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}怎么走了
Dialogue: 0,0:27:37.28,0:27:40.34,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}小女更衣 去去便来
Dialogue: 0,0:27:40.49,0:27:43.42,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}她更 更衣
Dialogue: 0,0:27:43.75,0:27:44.91,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}更衣
Dialogue: 0,0:27:49.06,0:27:52.15,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}更衣好 更衣好啊
Dialogue: 0,0:27:52.93,0:27:55.36,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}相国 请饮 请饮
Dialogue: 0,0:27:57.13,0:28:02.54,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}这个 貂蝉今年多大了
Dialogue: 0,0:28:03.31,0:28:04.87,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}十七
Dialogue: 0,0:28:05.98,0:28:07.27,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}请饮
Dialogue: 0,0:28:07.51,0:28:12.31,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}十七 十七好哇
Dialogue: 0,0:28:12.38,0:28:13.91,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}王允啊 你看
Dialogue: 0,0:28:14.32,0:28:15.72,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}这 这么一个大美人儿
Dialogue: 0,0:28:15.82,0:28:17.29,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}你把她搁在家里
Dialogue: 0,0:28:17.39,0:28:19.45,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}那是不是太可惜了
Dialogue: 0,0:28:19.89,0:28:21.05,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}可惜
Dialogue: 0,0:28:22.63,0:28:24.83,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}相国的意思是
Dialogue: 0,0:28:24.83,0:28:27.63,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}咱家的意 咱家的意思是这样的
Dialogue: 0,0:28:27.70,0:28:28.56,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}对了
Dialogue: 0,0:28:28.73,0:28:32.26,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}这个 当今天子尚未婚配
Dialogue: 0,0:28:32.50,0:28:36.13,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}貂蝉应该进宫嫁给天子做贵妃
Dialogue: 0,0:28:36.84,0:28:38.37,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}这可万万不成
Dialogue: 0,0:28:38.48,0:28:41.47,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}小女配不上天子啊
Dialogue: 0,0:28:41.55,0:28:44.04,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}配得上 配得上
Dialogue: 0,0:28:45.82,0:28:46.87,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}王允哪
Dialogue: 0,0:28:47.95,0:28:52.36,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}咱家今天要给貂蝉做个大媒
Dialogue: 0,0:28:53.39,0:28:56.12,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}要让她进宫嫁给天子做贵妃
Dialogue: 0,0:28:56.43,0:28:59.92,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}这事儿就这么定了
Dialogue: 0,0:29:01.37,0:29:04.23,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}那老臣谢恩
Dialogue: 0,0:29:06.00,0:29:07.73,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}好好好
Dialogue: 0,0:29:09.71,0:29:10.61,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}请
Dialogue: 0,0:29:14.31,0:29:19.58,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}这个 过两天 不 不不不
Dialogue: 0,0:29:20.28,0:29:22.22,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}就是今天晚上
Dialogue: 0,0:29:22.32,0:29:27.31,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}咱家派皇车来接貂蝉进宫
Dialogue: 0,0:29:27.46,0:29:29.05,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}今天
Dialogue: 0,0:29:30.46,0:29:31.79,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}禀相国
Dialogue: 0,0:29:32.16,0:29:36.26,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}天子大婚岂能说办就办
Dialogue: 0,0:29:36.33,0:29:39.53,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}依礼得要先下圣旨
Dialogue: 0,0:29:39.97,0:29:41.91,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}再赐聘书
Dialogue: 0,0:29:42.67,0:29:44.54,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}告天祭祖
Dialogue: 0,0:29:44.84,0:29:48.40,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}诏知百官及天下子民
Dialogue: 0,0:29:48.48,0:29:53.47,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}然后再选择良辰吉日举行大婚
Dialogue: 0,0:29:53.55,0:29:57.08,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}算下来怎么也得百日之后
Dialogue: 0,0:29:58.52,0:30:00.75,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}眼下是世道纷乱
Dialogue: 0,0:30:01.73,0:30:04.42,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}诸事可以从简嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:30:05.03,0:30:08.02,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}再说了 天子也等不及了嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:30:09.47,0:30:11.77,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}天子等不及了
Dialogue: 0,0:30:14.14,0:30:15.77,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}我看这样吧
Dialogue: 0,0:30:16.94,0:30:19.00,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}这个是急了一点啊
Dialogue: 0,0:30:19.44,0:30:21.64,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}改 改在后天
Dialogue: 0,0:30:23.01,0:30:27.64,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}咱家也要为天子做些准备呀
Dialogue: 0,0:30:29.59,0:30:30.68,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}遵命
Dialogue: 0,0:30:40.30,0:30:42.03,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}吕将军 这
Dialogue: 0,0:30:44.30,0:30:46.83,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}王司徒 你把貂蝉许配给我
Dialogue: 0,0:30:46.94,0:30:48.70,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}为何又送给相国
Dialogue: 0,0:30:48.77,0:30:51.14,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}将军 我正在等你呀
Dialogue: 0,0:30:51.24,0:30:53.47,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}你听我跟你说 你放手
Dialogue: 0,0:30:53.61,0:30:57.10,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}请到屋里 我好好跟你说清楚
Dialogue: 0,0:30:57.18,0:30:59.08,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}屋里好好说
Dialogue: 0,0:31:01.22,0:31:02.71,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}请
Dialogue: 0,0:31:07.93,0:31:10.66,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}将军息怒 将军息怒
Dialogue: 0,0:31:11.73,0:31:15.26,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}今日下朝以后相国突然造访
Dialogue: 0,0:31:15.53,0:31:18.37,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}说是来我这儿饮酒赏梅
Dialogue: 0,0:31:19.00,0:31:23.80,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}并且他亲点貂蝉伴宴
Dialogue: 0,0:31:23.84,0:31:26.47,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}你说老夫我岂敢不从
Dialogue: 0,0:31:27.48,0:31:29.57,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}谁人不知相国好色
Dialogue: 0,0:31:31.45,0:31:33.35,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}貂蝉美若天仙
Dialogue: 0,0:31:34.02,0:31:36.21,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}他只要一见貂蝉肯定垂涎三尺
Dialogue: 0,0:31:36.59,0:31:38.58,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}将军说得对啊
Dialogue: 0,0:31:38.76,0:31:43.52,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}相国见了貂蝉以后不饮自醉
Dialogue: 0,0:31:44.93,0:31:47.90,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}席未竟就下令说
Dialogue: 0,0:31:48.97,0:31:54.06,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}如此天仙凡人岂可贪求
Dialogue: 0,0:31:54.24,0:31:56.76,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}搁在家里可惜了
Dialogue: 0,0:31:57.07,0:32:03.01,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}应该敬献给汉帝立为贵妃啊
Dialogue: 0,0:32:04.58,0:32:07.92,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}什么 让貂蝉做贵妃
Dialogue: 0,0:32:09.65,0:32:15.82,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}真要能做贵妃老夫也无话可说
Dialogue: 0,0:32:16.16,0:32:17.68,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}老夫担心的是
Dialogue: 0,0:32:18.33,0:32:19.32,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}你担心什么
Dialogue: 0,0:32:21.70,0:32:24.76,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}老夫担心小女进不了皇宫
Dialogue: 0,0:32:24.80,0:32:29.83,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}最终进了相国的郿坞啊
Dialogue: 0,0:32:30.01,0:32:31.34,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}那绝对不行
Dialogue: 0,0:32:31.61,0:32:34.48,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}可 这 事已至此
Dialogue: 0,0:32:35.71,0:32:37.77,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}老夫有什么办法
Dialogue: 0,0:32:37.98,0:32:43.61,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}相国是代天子下的旨意
Dialogue: 0,0:32:43.72,0:32:45.45,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}要立貂蝉为妃
Dialogue: 0,0:32:46.82,0:32:47.76,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}你说
Dialogue: 0,0:32:47.96,0:32:49.22,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}我这个做臣下的
Dialogue: 0,0:32:49.39,0:32:52.16,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}敢不遵从天子的旨意吗
Dialogue: 0,0:32:54.73,0:32:57.10,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}就好比你做将军的
Dialogue: 0,0:32:57.47,0:33:00.06,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}敢违杭相国的谕令吗
Dialogue: 0,0:33:00.17,0:33:01.70,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}貂蝉在哪儿
Dialogue: 0,0:33:05.14,0:33:07.04,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}让我见见她
Dialogue: 0,0:33:08.21,0:33:13.08,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}将军啊 恕老夫提醒你一句
Dialogue: 0,0:33:13.92,0:33:18.32,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}貂蝉已经是贵妃之身了
Dialogue: 0,0:33:18.52,0:33:21.12,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}将军可万不能坏了
Dialogue: 0,0:33:21.39,0:33:24.09,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}朝廷的礼法啊
Dialogue: 0,0:33:28.73,0:33:30.06,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}我求你了
Dialogue: 0,0:33:33.60,0:33:34.90,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}义父
Dialogue: 0,0:33:36.31,0:33:38.67,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}我求你让我见貂蝉一面
Dialogue: 0,0:33:39.51,0:33:40.98,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}我求你了
Dialogue: 0,0:33:48.25,0:33:49.58,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}好吧
Dialogue: 0,0:33:51.89,0:33:57.33,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}你们 你们就见一面吧
Dialogue: 0,0:34:03.33,0:34:06.20,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}我们到底该怎么办
Dialogue: 0,0:34:06.90,0:34:09.74,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}貂蝉不愿意进宫为妃
Dialogue: 0,0:34:11.28,0:34:14.44,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}我只想和将军在一起
Dialogue: 0,0:34:15.25,0:34:21.15,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}生死相守 永不分离
Dialogue: 0,0:34:23.89,0:34:25.88,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}我也离不开你呀
Dialogue: 0,0:34:27.49,0:34:33.73,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}没有你我一天也活不下去
Dialogue: 0,0:34:34.27,0:34:39.03,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}将军真应该早点来
Dialogue: 0,0:34:39.20,0:34:43.64,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}真应该昨天就把貂蝉接走
Dialogue: 0,0:34:43.67,0:34:45.14,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}是我的错
Dialogue: 0,0:34:48.21,0:34:53.24,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}我来迟了 来迟了
Dialogue: 0,0:34:55.92,0:34:58.41,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}生生世世都在一起
Dialogue: 0,0:34:58.52,0:35:00.89,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}永远都不要分离
Dialogue: 0,0:35:00.99,0:35:05.43,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}女儿啊 快快照我教你的说啊
Dialogue: 0,0:35:22.98,0:35:27.18,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}将军 貂蝉命苦
Dialogue: 0,0:35:28.35,0:35:33.72,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}这辈子无法侍奉将军了
Dialogue: 0,0:35:35.56,0:35:41.76,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}只有下辈子再和将军长相厮守
Dialogue: 0,0:35:48.37,0:35:51.54,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}你就忘了貂蝉吧
Dialogue: 0,0:36:05.46,0:36:09.59,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}大雁高飞 成双成对
Dialogue: 0,0:36:11.93,0:36:13.66,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}若有一只离去
Dialogue: 0,0:36:16.70,0:36:19.69,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}爱侣必将不食而亡
Dialogue: 0,0:36:21.14,0:36:22.83,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}吕布愿与小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:36:24.27,0:36:26.40,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}同生共死
Dialogue: 0,0:36:27.51,0:36:29.41,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}无怨无悔
Dialogue: 0,0:36:30.58,0:36:32.21,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}将军
Dialogue: 0,0:36:50.23,0:36:53.67,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}好 说得好
Dialogue: 0,0:36:54.71,0:36:57.97,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}比我教的更好
Dialogue: 0,0:37:27.20,0:37:30.54,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}禀将军 尚父午睡未醒
Dialogue: 0,0:37:31.04,0:37:33.87,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}请将军稍候再来
Dialogue: 0,0:37:34.75,0:37:38.20,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}不 我在这儿等候
Dialogue: 0,0:37:38.78,0:37:41.65,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}那么请将军大堂待茶
Dialogue: 0,0:37:41.75,0:37:45.09,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}不 我就在这儿跪着
Dialogue: 0,0:37:46.59,0:37:48.72,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}喏
Dialogue: 0,0:37:55.17,0:37:57.22,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}禀尚父 温侯吕布
Dialogue: 0,0:37:57.67,0:38:00.10,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}在外头跪候了两个时辰了
Dialogue: 0,0:38:00.20,0:38:02.80,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}跪候 他干吗跪着
Dialogue: 0,0:38:02.87,0:38:06.97,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}这 奴才不知 将军也不肯说
Dialogue: 0,0:38:11.42,0:38:12.25,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}叫他进来吧
Dialogue: 0,0:38:12.35,0:38:13.91,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}喏
Dialogue: 0,0:38:24.36,0:38:26.66,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}吕将军 尚父有情
Dialogue: 0,0:38:47.89,0:38:51.51,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}奉先 听说你在外边儿跪候
Dialogue: 0,0:38:52.42,0:38:54.29,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}这到底是为什么呢
Dialogue: 0,0:38:55.93,0:39:00.12,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}儿臣有件事想请义父开恩
Dialogue: 0,0:39:00.46,0:39:05.83,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}说 只管说 说什么我都答应你
Dialogue: 0,0:39:09.07,0:39:10.44,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}义父
Dialogue: 0,0:39:10.67,0:39:13.07,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}请你看在我多年战功的份上
Dialogue: 0,0:39:14.61,0:39:18.17,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}把貂蝉赏给我
Dialogue: 0,0:39:23.69,0:39:24.81,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}貂蝉
Dialogue: 0,0:39:24.92,0:39:28.69,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}义父 儿臣喜欢她
Dialogue: 0,0:39:30.16,0:39:34.19,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}儿臣这辈子没有她不行
Dialogue: 0,0:39:35.03,0:39:38.23,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}什么话 什么叫没她不行
Dialogue: 0,0:39:38.60,0:39:39.86,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}男子汉大丈夫
Dialogue: 0,0:39:39.97,0:39:42.77,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}岂能为一女子折了志气
Dialogue: 0,0:39:42.87,0:39:44.47,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}起来
Dialogue: 0,0:39:45.21,0:39:46.30,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}义父
Dialogue: 0,0:39:51.58,0:39:53.11,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}你起来
Dialogue: 0,0:40:07.76,0:40:13.50,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}奉先哪 咱家跟你说实话
Dialogue: 0,0:40:13.90,0:40:16.40,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}别说是一个小小貂蝉
Dialogue: 0,0:40:16.77,0:40:18.47,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}你就是一百个貂蝉
Dialogue: 0,0:40:18.58,0:40:21.01,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}义父也舍得呀
Dialogue: 0,0:40:24.31,0:40:27.34,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}义父答应儿臣啦
Dialogue: 0,0:40:30.49,0:40:34.15,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}只可惜啊 你来晚了一步
Dialogue: 0,0:40:34.66,0:40:37.02,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}昨儿个咱家已经上奏天子
Dialogue: 0,0:40:37.13,0:40:39.43,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}把貂蝉送去做贵妃娘娘了
Dialogue: 0,0:40:39.56,0:40:42.26,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}朝中的百官都知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:40:44.50,0:40:46.80,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}奉先儿啊 你应该知道
Dialogue: 0,0:40:47.00,0:40:49.20,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}那些个公卿大臣们哪
Dialogue: 0,0:40:49.44,0:40:51.74,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}他都怨咱们不敬天子
Dialogue: 0,0:40:51.88,0:40:53.71,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}心里边儿恨着咱们呢
Dialogue: 0,0:40:54.11,0:40:57.55,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}你说咱们把貂蝉送去做贵妃娘娘
Dialogue: 0,0:40:57.71,0:41:00.18,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}这样的话一则是百官高兴
Dialogue: 0,0:41:00.32,0:41:02.84,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}二则天子也感谢咱们哪
Dialogue: 0,0:41:02.95,0:41:04.75,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}你说是不是
Dialogue: 0,0:41:07.16,0:41:09.63,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}奉先哪 这样吧
Dialogue: 0,0:41:10.26,0:41:13.79,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}你看咱们宫中除了貂蝉以外
Dialogue: 0,0:41:13.96,0:41:17.83,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}所有的宫女嫔妃任你挑选
Dialogue: 0,0:41:17.93,0:41:19.13,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}你要谁是谁
Dialogue: 0,0:41:19.27,0:41:21.57,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}你要多少是多少
Dialogue: 0,0:41:21.74,0:41:22.97,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}行不行
Dialogue: 0,0:41:46.03,0:41:55.42,lrc,,0,0,0,,{\blur2\fad(300,300)}天地之间莽苍苍
Dialogue: 0,0:41:55.42,0:42:06.52,lrc,,0,0,0,,{\blur2\fad(300,300)}一时多少豪强
Dialogue: 0,0:42:06.52,0:42:12.94,lrc,,0,0,0,,{\blur2\fad(300,300)}胜负由来不久长
Dialogue: 0,0:42:12.94,0:42:22.35,lrc,,0,0,0,,{\blur2\fad(300,300)}去如大江水
Dialogue: 0,0:42:22.35,0:42:34.27,lrc,,0,0,0,,{\blur2\fad(300,300)}奔流向远方
Dialogue: 0,0:42:50.97,0:42:59.85,lrc,,0,0,0,,{\blur2\fad(300,300)}书藏万卷胸次广
Dialogue: 0,0:42:59.85,0:43:12.08,lrc,,0,0,0,,{\blur2\fad(300,300)}细数百代兴亡
Dialogue: 0,0:43:12.08,0:43:17.95,lrc,,0,0,0,,{\blur2\fad(300,300)}功成身退早还乡
Dialogue: 0,0:43:17.95,0:43:27.32,lrc,,0,0,0,,{\blur2\fad(300,300)}平淡心中事
Dialogue: 0,0:43:27.32,0:43:39.95,lrc,,0,0,0,,{\blur2\fad(300,300)}无语对斜阳
